#: 6e46b8981e304202bb80e9b01801a898 of
#: tensormesh.nn.buffer_dict.BufferDict.as_parameter:1
msgid ""
"Promote the buffer at ``key`` to a trainable :class:`torch.nn.Parameter` "
"in place."
msgstr ""

#: 57cd8f92dc954f0d90d2f6043d827a6a of
#: tensormesh.nn.buffer_dict.BufferDict.as_parameter:3
msgid ""
"After this call, ``self[key]`` is a Parameter (gradient-tracking, will "
"appear in :meth:`~torch.nn.Module.parameters`); the same key must "
"currently live in :attr:`_buffers` or this will raise ``KeyError``. "
"Reverse with :meth:`as_buffer`."
msgstr ""

#: 297fff3ed6954713bdf807d0d7fd27b4 of
#: tensormesh.nn.buffer_dict.BufferDict.as_buffer:1
msgid "Demote the parameter at ``key`` back to a (non-trainable) buffer in place."
msgstr ""

#: 8cc83fb67d98486b8b37308931fcf192 of
#: tensormesh.nn.buffer_dict.BufferDict.as_buffer:3
msgid ""
"Inverse of :meth:`as_parameter`. The same key must currently live in "
":attr:`_parameters`. The underlying storage is shared (via "
":meth:`~torch.Tensor.detach`); the result no longer requires grad."
msgstr ""

#: f49d60468811410ca3f235a5923d5df9 of
#: tensormesh.nn.buffer_dict.BufferDict.keys:1
msgid ""
"Iterate over keys across all three backing stores (buffers, parameters, "
